definitions.definition: The person or thing in the eighth position .
One of eight equal parts of a whole.
examples: Two bits equals two eighths of a dollar.

definitions.definition: An eighth of an ounce , or approximately 3.5 grams, of marijuana or other drugs.
An interval by doubling in pitch frequency.
